Dear {!Case.Contact},
You now have access to the following Markit Securities Finance applications:
<enter product list here>
Please click on the following links to access:
- DX Open; <https://msf.markit.com/Portal> - Evaluation Explorer; <https://msf.markit.com/Ex> - International Index Explorer; <https://msf.markit.com/IIX> - Performance Explorer; <https://msf.markit.com/Px> - Risk Explorer; <https://msf.markit.com/risk/rx> - SF One; <https://msf.markit.com/Portal/?Mode=DxOne> - Transaction Explorer; <https://msf.markit.com/Tx> - UK Index Explorer; <https://msf.markit.com/IX>
Your username is: <enter user name here>
For security reasons, the password will be provided to you in a separate email shortly.
Please Note:
1. In order to install the Markit Securities Finance Toolkit for Microsoft Excel on your PC, please contact the relevant Deutsche Bank Market Data team, identified below: London - EMEA-MDS.Requests@db.com Frankfurt - GER-MDS.Requests@db.com AsiaPac - AP-MDS.Requests@db.com North America - NA-MDS.Requests@db.com Hong Kong - HK-MDS.Request@db.com India - INDIA-MDS.Requests@db.com
2. All usernames and passwords are case sensitive
3. For security reasons, the password will be provided to you in a separate email shortly.
Please note, by logging in and installing the Toolkit for Microsoft Excel you are agreeing to our Trial Terms and/or Terms of Business.
Also attached with this email are the following documents which you may find useful:
1. A post-install checking sheet 2. A user guide for the Toolkit Navigator
If you require any additional assistance, please contact us on live chat, email or phone.
Thank You.
Kind regards, {!Case.OwnerFirstName} {!Case.OwnerLastName} Markit Securities Finance UK: +44 808 120 2344 | US: +1 866 861 6171 | HK: +852 800 964 146 msf-support@markit.com
